Got 650k followers in Tiktok. 
An interesting finding:
For image generation, gemini's nano banana is the king. All other models are just good to be the followers...
For video generation, there are many choices, veo3 is a good choice, sora2 was once the king but "dead" now... models from china like alibaba/bytedance/kling are evolving quickly, especially seedance 2.0 - which is considered a GPT-moment in video generation.&lt;p&gt;Anyone here works with AI videos too?&lt;/p&gt;
